Requirements
************

    Twilight Development System @{b}TDS@{ub} 2.12 runs on any Amiga with
Kickstart 2.04 (V37) and greater. If available, it will use the
@{b}locale.library@{ub} to support localization. It can also use the
@{b}reqtools.library@{ub} V38, but the library is not required to run the
software.


@EndNode

