Installation
************

    To install @{b}TDS@{ub} you can use the @{b}Installer@{ub} program from Commodore. To
start the installation process simply double-click the icon called
@{b}Install TDS@{ub} and follow the instructions. The installation script will
modify your @{b}user-startup@{ub} to include an assignment to the directory
containing the programs which will be called @{b}TDS:@{ub}. You have also the
choice to install some example project files which will help you in
building your own project files.

    If you don't have the @{b}Installer@{ub} program, then you can manually
install the software creating a directory and copying there all files.
Finally add an @{b}assign TDS: <your directory>@{ub} to the file @{b}user-startup@{ub}.


@EndNode

