Twilight Editor (Ted)
*********************

    This is the main program of the package. It can be run from either
the Workbench or the Shell. When running on the Workbench screen @{b}Ted@{ub}
will open its windows as AppWindows which means that if you want to
open a file, just drop its icon into one of the windows and the file
will be loaded.


