Search/Find
-----------

    Open a requester to enter the string to search for and with the
following search options:

@{b}Case Sensitive@{ub}
     Distinguishes between upper and lower case.

@{b}Words Only@{ub}
     Finds only strings surrounded by spaces.

@{b}Wildcards@{ub}
     Uses '?' as a wildcard which matches any character.
          e.g. @{b}t??t@{ub} matches @{b}test@{ub}, @{b}that@{ub}, etc.

@{b}Special@{ub}
     Uses '\\' as an escape character to find and replace special
     characters like:

          '\\b' backspace
          '\\f' formfeed
          '\\t' horizontal tab
          '\\v' vertical tab
